---
import ThankYouLayout from '../../layouts/ThankYouLayout.astro';
---

<ThankYouLayout
  productSlug="agent-governance-starter-kit"
  description="Your Agent Governance Starter Kit is ready to download."
  readyLine="Your Agent Governance Starter Kit is ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your kit"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Agent-Governance-Starter-Kit-v1.0.pdf"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>The Agent Governance Starter Kit includes five governance layers: charter template, boundary specification, drift threshold framework, four-level accountability system, and authority structure template.</p>
    <p>Start with the Charter Template in Part 1. Everything else depends on it.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/agent-governance-starter-kit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Write your charter</h3>
      <p>Use the template to define your core beliefs and essential properties. Test each belief against the three criteria in Part 1.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Open the kit page &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/products/trust-architecture-blueprint" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Go deeper</h3>
      <p>Pair this with the Trust Architecture Blueprint for identity and memory architecture, or the Agent Restraint Specification Template for refusal boundaries.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">See the Blueprint &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/fit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Check your fit</h3>
      <p>A 5-minute fit assessment to see which Evoke services align with where you are right now.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Take the assessment &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://cal.com/cal.com-evoked/discovery-call" class="pd-upsell-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <h3>Talk it through</h3>
      <p>Book a free 30-minute discovery call to discuss your governance architecture.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Schedule &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </Fragment>
</ThankYouLayout>
